  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/20e41918d9117694.jpg?v=1782537731\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Woohoo - my tour is officially kicking off today! It's been something we have been planning and preparing for with <a href=\"http://www.heidiswapp.com/spotlight-selfie-grand-prize-contest/\">Spotlight</a> down under for a while now, and finally it’s time! As part of the festivities… <a href=\"http://www.heidiswapp.com/\">Heidi Swapp</a> and I thought that it would be fun to have some GIVEAWAYS! Last month I went to Utah and Heidi and I spent the morning together crafting away in the studio! We know that not everyone will be able to get to a store where we will be doing make &amp; takes and demos… but we totally wanted everyone down under to be able to play along during <a href=\"http://www.heidiswapp.com/spotlight-selfie-grand-prize-contest/\">Spotlights’ National Craft Month celebrations</a> AND have a chance to WIN! -</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/16c21fa185427cd6.jpg?v=1782537733\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Here’s what we are giving away, there will be 26 LUCKY winners!</p><p><strong>25 Winners</strong> will receive 2 lovely FOILED prints! Both Heidi and I designed an 8 ½ x11 print and we signed each one!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c256a70a49733d36.jpg?v=1782537737\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5c61f30faf8f0b72.jpg?v=1782537739\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>1 GRAND PRIZE WINNER will receive the SUPER AWESOME Marquee sign that Heidi and I crafted together! We used her amazing new “Marquee Love” letter lights, and my new “Rise &amp; Shine” collection to spell out: RISE &amp; SHINE!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d518812e076720f3.jpg?v=1782537742\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Here’s how you can ENTER to win!</p><p>1. Go to the nearest <a href=\"http://spotlight.com.au/\">Spotlight</a> store, and take a selfie with either of our products carried in the store!</p><p>2. Upload your photo to Instagram and use the hashtag: #SpotlightNCMwin</p><p>3. Tag @amytangerine, @hkswapp and @spotlightstores so we can see your smiling faces!</p><p>4. Keep your eye out… winners will be notified via Instagram! You will be contacted for your mailing address.</p><p>I LOVE seeing my new products hitting shelves. And then I also love seeing how you all use the collection items in such creative ways! Please be sure to tag me up so I can get a glimpse! I’d love to meet up with you in real life – so come and say hello when <a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/2015/2/5/heading-to-australia-in-march.html\">I am hanging out at the SPOTLIGHT store nearest you</a>! Until then, be sure you follow me - <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/amytangerine\">@amytangerine</a> and <a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkswapp/\">@hkswapp</a> on Instagram and I’ll see you soon! Can't wait to see your Spotlight selfie!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}